# Day 33 - Media Integrity Analyzer

## Objective

Build an AI-powered Media Integrity Analyzer to evaluate news headlines, detect emotional manipulation, and improve media literacy through interactive challenges.

---

## Features

- Theme Selection
- Headline Detective Challenge
- AI Headline Analysis
- Headline Rewriting
- Emotion Detector
- Emotional Manipulation Analysis
- Live Media Integrity Metrics
- Final Media Integrity Dashboard
- Randomized News Scenarios

---

## Workflow

1. Started the simulator.
2. Selected a preferred color theme.
3. Completed the Headline Detective challenge.
4. Reviewed AI-generated headline analysis.
5. Compared the rewritten neutral headline.
6. Completed the Emotion Detector challenge.
7. Studied emotional manipulation techniques.
8. Observed live Media Integrity metrics.
9. Reviewed the final dashboard.
10. Replayed different randomized scenarios.

